                <h1>Understanding GMOs: Benefits & Concerns</h1>
                <p>Genetically modified organisms (GMOs) are organisms whose genetic material has been altered using biotechnology. This innovation aims to enhance food production, resistance to pests, and nutritional value. While GMOs offer potential benefits, they also raise concerns about environmental impact and health risks, sparking ongoing debate.</p>
